WEBVTT

00:04.210 --> 00:05.830
Yes, chilling!

00:05.960 --> 00:09.590
I'm so scared of your leftover
prop from a Styx video.

00:09.710 --> 00:12.970
Oh, please spare my life, Mr. Roboto.

00:15.890 --> 00:17.180
Miss me, darling?

00:17.300 --> 00:19.720
What? No, I just saw you,
like, five minutes ago.

00:19.850 --> 00:22.930
You have thwarted my robot,
my dear Monarch!

00:23.060 --> 00:26.940
But Dr. Dugong has plenty more
tricks up his sleeve.

00:27.060 --> 00:28.060
You don't have sleeves.

00:28.190 --> 00:29.610
You're in a seal costume.

00:29.730 --> 00:30.650
Dugong!

00:30.780 --> 00:32.570
And it's not a costume!

00:32.689 --> 00:35.450
- Boys, locate Dr. Manatee.
- Dugong!

00:35.570 --> 00:37.660
He's been on the stupid PA
the whole time.

00:37.780 --> 00:39.240
There's a speaker right
over my head.

00:39.370 --> 00:40.580
It's so loud.

00:40.700 --> 00:41.910
It's blah, blah blah, blah blah.

00:42.040 --> 00:44.250
...desperate attempt to learn
the secrets of love and caring,

00:44.370 --> 00:47.500
was chemically fused
with a gentle sea cow!

00:47.630 --> 00:50.040
Dr. Sea Lion won't stop
with the third person.

00:50.170 --> 00:51.090
Dugong!

00:51.210 --> 00:52.250
A dugong!

00:52.380 --> 00:53.710
Douglas Ong.

00:53.840 --> 00:55.380
Dr. Dugong --

00:55.510 --> 00:56.880
Oh, my God, thank you.

00:57.010 --> 00:59.550
OK, I know he's annoying,
but you have to get into it.

00:59.680 --> 01:01.390
You gotta at least pretend to try.

01:01.510 --> 01:02.680
He's such a weenus.

01:02.810 --> 01:04.769
Did you hear that origin story?

01:04.890 --> 01:07.520
"Secrets of love and caring"?

01:07.650 --> 01:09.350
- "Caring"?
- Yeah, that was kinda gay.

01:09.480 --> 01:12.270
But I really want you to try
to take this seriously.

01:12.400 --> 01:14.940
We've located Dr. Dugong, mum.

01:15.070 --> 01:17.530
Good work.
Mommy's little babies.

01:17.660 --> 01:19.490
It's bad enough
that they ignore me...

01:19.620 --> 01:20.950
but do you have to call them that?

01:21.080 --> 01:24.540
Man seeks a good time,
but he is not a hedonist.

01:24.660 --> 01:28.500
He seeks love,
he just doesn't know where to look.

01:28.630 --> 01:29.880
He looks under the beds...

01:30.000 --> 01:33.590
of whores and in the hot stem
of a crack pipe...

01:33.710 --> 01:35.420
but he should look to nature.

01:35.550 --> 01:39.890
Gentle aquatic mammals
have all the answers.

01:41.100 --> 01:43.810
Your door was locked,
so we let ourselves in.

01:43.930 --> 01:45.520
Yeah, we got our own key.

01:45.640 --> 01:48.350
Well, if it isn't Dr. Mrs. The Monarch...

01:48.480 --> 01:51.810
the pupa twins, and... a-and...

01:51.940 --> 01:53.650
Come on, Monarch. What's the holdup?

01:53.780 --> 01:55.230
OK, OK.

01:55.360 --> 01:58.320
Oh, man! You're all flesh colored.

01:58.450 --> 02:00.360
How much thalidomide
did your mom take?

02:00.490 --> 02:03.530
You may have found
my inner sanctum, but you are not --

02:03.660 --> 02:04.580
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

02:04.700 --> 02:05.990
Can you hold that speech
for a second?

02:06.120 --> 02:07.450
- Don't forget it.
- I won't.

02:07.580 --> 02:08.870
One second!

02:09.000 --> 02:10.919
Will you just try to do this right?

02:11.039 --> 02:11.960
This guy's a chump.

02:12.090 --> 02:13.380
You get me in front of Dr. Venture...

02:13.500 --> 02:14.710
and I'll show you how I dance.

02:14.840 --> 02:17.210
We'll talk about that later.
Now, please, do it for me.

02:17.340 --> 02:20.220
OK, fine.

02:20.340 --> 02:21.470
Go ahead.

02:21.590 --> 02:24.850
Oh, oh. You may have found
my inner sanctum --

02:24.970 --> 02:28.140
Shut up! Now give us the key, or the plans
or whatever-the-hell you have!

02:28.270 --> 02:31.560
I have a tank full of gentle cuttlefish.

02:31.690 --> 02:33.690
Give us the cuttlefish!

02:33.820 --> 02:35.150
Cuttle...

02:35.280 --> 02:36.360
I can't do this!

02:36.480 --> 02:38.530
Oh, you were so close, sweetie.

02:38.650 --> 02:40.820
Just pretend he's Dr. Venture.

02:42.490 --> 02:44.870
Give me that gun.

02:46.330 --> 02:48.330
You abandoned me!

02:48.450 --> 02:50.370
You abandoned my hatred!

02:50.500 --> 02:51.920
I-I-I have cuttlefish.

02:52.040 --> 02:54.460
Look into my eyes!

